    <div class="container-fluid header bg-white p-0 mb-5">
        <div class="row g-0 align-items-center flex-column-reverse flex-lg-row">
            <div class="col-lg-6 p-5 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
                <h1 class="display-4 text-dark mb-5">Language is the key, the world is the treasure.</h1>
                <div class="row g-4">
                    <div class="col-sm-4">
                        <div class="border-start border-light ps-4">
                            <h2 class="text-dark mb-1" data-toggle="counter-up">356</h2>
                            <p class="text-dark mb-0">Expert Teachers</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-4">
                        <div class="border-start border-light ps-4">
                            <h2 class="text-dark mb-1" data-toggle="counter-up">12345</h2>
                            <p class="text-dark mb-0">Total Learners</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.5s">
                <div class="owl-carousel header-carousel">
                    <div class="owl-carousel-item position-relative">
                        <img class="img-fluid" src="images/64664.jpg" alt="">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-xxl py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-sm-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
                    <div class="service-item text-center pt-3">
                        <div class="p-4">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-3x fa-graduation-cap mb-4"></i>
                            <h5 class="mb-3">Skilled Instructors</h5>
                            <p>
                                Our online platform offers lessons at different levels and in a variety of languages with expert instructors from around the world. Whether you are starting to learn a new language or want to improve your advanced skills, our experienced and passionate instructors are ready to guide you. We are here to help you achieve your goals with a quality and interactive educational experience.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-sm-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.3s">
                    <div class="service-item text-center pt-3">
                        <div class="p-4">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-3x fa-globe mb-4"></i>
                            <h5 class="mb-3">Online Classes</h5>
                            <p>
                                Do you have a busy schedule? No problem! All our courses give you flexible learning opportunities without time constraints. Attend live lectures, watch recorded training videos and practice - all online.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-sm-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.7s">
                    <div class="service-item text-center pt-3">
                        <div class="p-4">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-3x fa-book-open mb-4"></i>
                            <h5 class="mb-3">Book Library</h5>
                            <p>
                                Make your learning process more enjoyable and effective with carefully selected books, course materials, visual guides and multimedia content for every language and level. There are resources suitable for all users, from beginner to advanced. Find the right content for you, set your learning goals and progress at your own pace.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-sm-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.5s">
                    <div class="service-item text-center pt-3">
                        <div class="p-4">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-3x fa-globe  mb-4"></i>
                            <h5 class="mb-3">Home Projects</h5>
                            <p>
                                Online meetings allow you to make new friends, learn about different accents and expressions, and use the language you are learning in a natural way. Whether you want to discuss a project, have casual conversations or have in-depth conversations about your interests, Global Language Hub offers you a rich communication experience. Join, talk and explore the world from your home.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
